Very low social and economic system established in my country, very hard climate, without sun during winter and without water on property level during summer, big and complicated work, little or no time for myself, personal level and quiet building our dream on self-responsible, sustainable level. I think, that's a big problem of our province.

Todate I practiced a lot of medieval and modernity martial arts. I hold amature belts and skill level in three types of martial arts and I am waiting for European competition in freestyle with martial arts character this year. But I only wish, that our team would train and have enough physical, mental, social luxury to prepare to defend our laud of Slavonic, Balkans Team and one day to win glory of Europeans Warrior in Kung Fu and Wushu. Thanks for your work. Have a good day.
